summary:
This is a resource for modders who want to either finish or pick from. comes with meshes and textures, though the meshes are not game ready (needs to be re-skinned ect).
All meshes (save for the CBBE body and the Satchel + waterskin straps) are of my own creation, please credit me if you use them.
descriptionHtml:
Due to software licenses and my constant procrastinating I may not finish this project, so I am uploading the files here for others to either finish, or pick apart for their own mods.
Please credit me if you use any of the meshes or textures, (not including the body ofcourse, thats caliente's work) also credit for bethesda for the meshes that the waterskin straps and the satchel are made from.

Hope at the least someone gets some use out of this.
author: SkyrimForDaWin
